<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2023-11-23T06:15:09-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2023-11-23T06:15:09-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-23T06:15:09-05:00</updated><title>微软，我们可以直接称其为 Windows 11.1 吗？</title><content type="html"> &lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ay5n_AlOVzCcrPKfwehb-_YOzJY=/0x0:1650x1100/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /72895204/windows11main.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Microsoft&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;QsJ5kr&quot;>;每次看到 Windows 11 重大更新时，我都想知道为什么它不是一个重大更新Windows 11.1 或 Windows 11.2 版本。相反，微软近年来使用了许多令人困惑的方式来命名Windows更新，而不是像点发布这样的简单方法。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Qiolrp&quot;>;让我向您说明我的&lt;em>;观点&lt;/em>;：&lt;/p>; &lt;ul>; &lt;li id=&quot;zbeebu&quot;>;Windows 10 周年更新&lt;/li>; &lt;li id=&quot;Liy498&quot;>;Windows 10 创意者更新&lt;/li>; &lt;li id=&quot;KYVOTk&quot;>;Windows 10 秋季创意者更新&lt;/li>; &lt;li id=&quot;Y4evL3&quot;>;Windows 10 2020 年 10 月更新&lt;/li>; &lt;li id=&quot;Hpy0Ky&quot;>;Windows 10 2021 年 5 月更新&lt;/li>; &lt;li id=&quot;GLhykj&quot;>;Windows 11 22H2&lt;/li>; &lt;li id=&quot;xg2b02&quot;>;Windows 11 2023 更新&lt;/li>; &lt;/ ul>; &lt;p id=&quot;nMETrz&quot;>;如您所见，微软正在逐渐为 Windows 版本制定更易于理解的命名策略，但它仍然经常使用 22H2 和 23H2 绰号，这对普通人来说听起来很奇怪。如果您进入 Windows 更新，您也更有可能看到...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/23/23973670/microsoft- windows-11-point-release-updates-pretty-please-thank-you-love-tom&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/23/23973670/microsoft-windows-11-point-release-updates-pretty-please-thank-you-love-tom" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/23/23973670/microsoft-windows-11-point-release-updates-pretty-please-thank-you-love-tom</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-23T05:35:41-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-23T05:35:41-05:00</updated><title>屏幕共享错误导致英伟达因涉嫌窃取商业机密而被起诉</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Nvidia 徽标。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/r47oCkc-xqkWSNp7VkL_BCZawlk=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72895147/acastro_STK083_01.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;由 Alex Castro / The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;pZCuSd&quot;>;如果您曾因公开分享不应该分享的屏幕部分而让自己感到尴尬，请想想 Mohammad Moniruzzaman，他被指控在与同一家公司进行 Microsoft Teams 通话时展示了他从前雇主那里窃取的源代码。 &lt;/em>;该事件已在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.documentcloud.org/documents/24174583-5_23-cv-05721?responsive=1&amp;amp;title=1&quot;>;诉讼中曝光&lt;/a >; 由 Moniruzzaman 的前雇主汽车技术公司法雷奥 (Valeo) 提起，该公司正在起诉 Nvidia（Moniruzzaman 转到的公司），并指控该公司从这些被盗的商业机密中受益。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;GSNnTn&quot;>;Nvidia 已十年来的大部分时间都在尝试进军汽车市场。法雷奥指控 Moniruzzaman“未经授权下载了法雷奥的全部高级停车和...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/23/23973673/valeo -nvidia-autonomous-driven-software-ip-theft-lawsuit&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/23/23973673/valeo-nvidia-autonomous-driving-software-ip-theft-lawsuit" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/23/23973673/valeo-nvidia-autonomous-driven-software-ip-theft-lawsuit</id><author><name>乔恩·波特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-22T17:14:57-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-22T17:14:57-05:00</updated><title> NLRB 声称苹果拒绝为工会工人提供更好的福利</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Apple 徽标的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/kFZmdBkxB8VbvnZa44cSZExk1Vo=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72893878/STK071_ACastro_apple_0003.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=