viceability-framework&quot;>;做出了...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23972676/steam-deck-oled-legion-go-teardown-ifixit-repairability-hall-effects-sticks&quot;>;继续阅读……&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23972676/steam-deck-oled-legion-go-teardown-ifixit-repairability-hall-effects-sticks" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23972676/steam-deck-oled-legion-go-teardown-ifixit-repairability-hall-effects-sticks</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-22T15:56:08-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-22T15:56:08-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 为爸爸们准备的 2023 年节日礼物指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;照片插图，手拿着各种产品，背景是明亮的星星。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/H7Tf9Gt9gLvu4O8O8J7kXzIfkyc=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72867725/236830_FOR_DAD_Gift_Guide_ Artboards_CVirginia_LEDE_2040x1360.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;由 Amelia Holowaty Krales 和 Cath Virginia / The Verge 拍摄的照片插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;我们为您生命中的所有爸爸收集了一系列有趣而独特的礼物创意，这样您就可以无论您的预算如何，都可以宠坏它们。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23947139/holiday-gifts-dad-unique-ideas-2023-tech-gadgets&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip ;&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23947139/holiday-gifts-dad-unique-ideas-2023-tech-gadgets" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23947139/holiday-gifts-dad-unique-ideas-2023-tech-gadgets</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-22T15:50:17-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-22T15:50:17-05:00</updated><title>这是目前最优惠的 iPad 优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;2020 iPad Air 和新款 iPad Mini 具有与 iPad Pro 相同的设计和形状&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/OqDG5sf2dQljUBF65yx​​BXRiy6oE=/0x0:2040x1360 /1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/